title: Egyptian ambassador pays farewell call on FM Jilani
content:
ISLAMABAD, Oct 13 (APP): Ambassador of Egypt in Islamabad Tarek Dahroug on Friday paid a farewell call on Caretaker Foreign Minister Jalil Abbas Jilani.
In the meeting, the foreign minister thanked the ambassador for his efforts in strengthening Pakistan-Egypt bilateral ties.
He also wished the ambassador well for his future endeavours.
